<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="418" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2123,776,1396]" pageId="0" pageNumber="418">• Stocky, robust, burrowing, plantigrade, pouched marsupials, with short thick necks, broad dorso-ventrally flattened skulls, small ears, large broad sacra, short and powerful limbs, and vestigial tails.</paragraph>
